---
title: Honey-Smoked Chicken Skewers with Sweet Potato Wedges (F)
description: It’s that point in the year when the nights are so cold you need to know there is a light (and a summer!) at the end of the tunnel. That’s why we’re giving you a hearty warming dinner with a little reminder of BBQ season. As ever, the longer you leave the chicken to marinade the better the flavour. Roll on summer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54b659e46ced6e567a8b4569.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/54b659e46ced6e567a8b4569.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/honey-smoked-chicken-skewers-54b659e46ced6e567a8b4569
